<h2>Taking care of business: resources for task management</h2>
<p>Carefully planning your tasks is an excellent way to achieve your work while maintaining spillover and stress at bay. Here are a few resources you can consult to help you improve your task management skills:</p>
<ul>
<li><a href="https://doist.com/blog/the-ultimate-guide-to-personal-productivity-methods/">Doist: The Ultimate Guide to Personal Productivity Methods</a></li>
<li><a href="https://zapier.com/blog/task-management-strategies/)">Zapier: Your To Do List and Beyond: 8 Powerful Ways to Manage Your Tasks</a></li>
<li><a href="https://hamberg.no/gtd/">Getting Things Done explained in 15 minutes</a></li>
<li><a href="https://youtu.be/gCswMsONkwY">Getting Things Done book: 8-minute illustrated video summary</a></li>
<li><a href="https://zenhabits.net/zen-to-done-ztd-the-ultimate-simple-productivity-system/">Zen To Done (ZTD): The Simple Productivity System</a></li>
</ul>
